  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bend fire, water, earth and air in chaotic online combat and co-op!<br><br>Elements Divided lets you become a peak elemental warrior. Command the battlefield with instinctive, gesture-based controls and defy gravity by hurling yourself across arenas. Unleash legendary powers through devastating elemental combos in frantic brawls with up to 8 players. Now with Sub-Elements, brand new Techniques, new Maps and tons of new Cosmetics!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RISE AS THE ULTIMATE ELEMENTAL BENDER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the world of bending and master all four elements—each with its own style and strategy. Unlock the hidden powers of Sub-Elements like Lava, Metal, Blood, Explosion and Spirit to take your bending to the next level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/a6fbfc6c3832a4c57e88543b46f69f42.poster.avif?t=1773805399\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/a6fbfc6c3832a4c57e88543b46f69f42.webm?t=1773805399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/a6fbfc6c3832a4c57e88543b46f69f42.mp4?t=1773805399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ENDLESS WAYS TO FIGHT</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash nearly 100 bending moves across Fire, Water, Earth, and Air. Hurl blazing fireballs, bend massive waves, summon powerful air shields, raise stone walls, and so much more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/4b3ca274a503e111ec294b9707a0bcff.poster.avif?t=1773805399\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/4b3ca274a503e111ec294b9707a0bcff.webm?t=1773805399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/4b3ca274a503e111ec294b9707a0bcff.mp4?t=1773805399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BATTLE IN CHAOS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump into wild online battles across tons of unique maps. Test your skills in PvP duels with up to 8 players, or team up with your crew to crush waves of enemies and bosses in epic showdowns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/f71c031df9d0b7e3869fd9826d064e57.poster.avif?t=1773805399\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/f71c031df9d0b7e3869fd9826d064e57.webm?t=1773805399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/f71c031df9d0b7e3869fd9826d064e57.mp4?t=1773805399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FORGE YOUR BENDER’S LEGEND</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rank up in each element to unlock new bending techniques and abilities. Personalize your bender with tons of customization options and show the world your unique elemental style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/5cb379e99da2945708f5164e59481451.poster.avif?t=1773805399\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/5cb379e99da2945708f5164e59481451.webm?t=1773805399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/5cb379e99da2945708f5164e59481451.mp4?t=1773805399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bend fire, water, earth and air in chaotic online combat and co-op!<br><br>Elements Divided lets you become a peak elemental warrior. Command the battlefield with instinctive, gesture-based controls and defy gravity by hurling yourself across arenas. Unleash legendary powers through devastating elemental combos in frantic brawls with up to 8 players. Now with Sub-Elements, brand new Techniques, new Maps and tons of new Cosmetics!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RISE AS THE ULTIMATE ELEMENTAL BENDER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the world of bending and master all four elements—each with its own style and strategy. Unlock the hidden powers of Sub-Elements like Lava, Metal, Blood, Explosion and Spirit to take your bending to the next level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/a6fbfc6c3832a4c57e88543b46f69f42.poster.avif?t=1773805399\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/a6fbfc6c3832a4c57e88543b46f69f42.webm?t=1773805399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/a6fbfc6c3832a4c57e88543b46f69f42.mp4?t=1773805399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ENDLESS WAYS TO FIGHT</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash nearly 100 bending moves across Fire, Water, Earth, and Air. Hurl blazing fireballs, bend massive waves, summon powerful air shields, raise stone walls, and so much more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/4b3ca274a503e111ec294b9707a0bcff.poster.avif?t=1773805399\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/4b3ca274a503e111ec294b9707a0bcff.webm?t=1773805399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/4b3ca274a503e111ec294b9707a0bcff.mp4?t=1773805399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BATTLE IN CHAOS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump into wild online battles across tons of unique maps. Test your skills in PvP duels with up to 8 players, or team up with your crew to crush waves of enemies and bosses in epic showdowns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/f71c031df9d0b7e3869fd9826d064e57.poster.avif?t=1773805399\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/f71c031df9d0b7e3869fd9826d064e57.webm?t=1773805399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/f71c031df9d0b7e3869fd9826d064e57.mp4?t=1773805399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FORGE YOUR BENDER’S LEGEND</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rank up in each element to unlock new bending techniques and abilities. Personalize your bender with tons of customization options and show the world your unique elemental style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/5cb379e99da2945708f5164e59481451.poster.avif?t=1773805399\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/5cb379e99da2945708f5164e59481451.webm?t=1773805399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805770/extras/5cb379e99da2945708f5164e59481451.mp4?t=1773805399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
